snippet.title: Trailer (Final) - Alice: Through the Fey Realm
snippet.description:
'Alice: Through the Fey Realm' is an enchanting isometric narrative adventure that thrusts you into the shoes of Alice. A compelling adventure unfolds as you awaken in the mysterious Fey Realm and embark on a quest to discover the key to your journey home.

This is latest (& final) trailer of 'Alice: Through the Fey Realm' which includes all the new updates to the game.

This project is made by 3rd year students from Breda University of Applied Sciences. It is free to play and can be downloaded on Steam for PC!

You can find the link to the game in our bio.
